				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "An AD that triggers when players interact with a deactivated soul pillar.\r\nThere are four different pillars in Foyer room, each one should have different description of what should happen with the souls inside. \r\nThe idea of AD to hint on what's happening to the souls that Raphael collects.\r\n\r\nIf players didn't succeed on a preceeding skillcheck, they don't learn anything about the souls."
				}
